'''Greg Knight''' is the cover artist who did the art for all the novels in the [[Republic Commando|''Republic Commando'' series]] and the concept art for ''[[Star Wars: Republic Commando]]'' and it has been confirmed that he did the cover art for the fourth book. He also created concept paintings and sketches for the canceled video game ''[[Star Wars: Imperial Commando]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed]]''.

